---
---
<section class="section media-section" id="media">
  <div class="media-bg"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-center reveal">
      <div class="media-badge">BOOKS & MEDIA</div>
      <h2 class="media-title">Rebooting the Brain — <span class="text-gradient">In Every Format</span></h2>
      <p class="media-sub">
        From a childhood fascination in Reader's Digest to a globally acclaimed body of work — Dr. Sharan communicates neuroscience through the language of tech, story, and soul.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="media-grid">
      <!-- Book -->
      <div class="media-card book-card reveal">
        <div class="media-icon-wrap book-icon-wrap">
          <span class="media-emoji">📘</span>
        </div>
        <div class="media-type-badge">AMAZON BESTSELLER</div>
        <h3 class="media-card-title">"Rebooting the Brain"</h3>
        <p class="media-card-sub">The Journey of Hope — Part 1</p>
        <p class="media-card-desc">
          Co-authored with Dr. Prathiba, this Amazon Bestseller uses the power of real patient stories to restore belief in healing, science, and the human spirit. "Every patient is not a case. Every patient is a story."
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="media-cta">Get the Book →</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Podcast -->
      <div class="media-card podcast-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="media-icon-wrap podcast-icon-wrap">
          <span class="media-emoji">🎙️</span>
        </div>
        <div class="media-type-badge podcast-badge">GLOBAL PODCAST</div>
        <h3 class="media-card-title">"Rebooting the Brain"</h3>
        <p class="media-card-sub">Launched December 14, 2024</p>
        <p class="media-card-desc">
          One of the most-watched neuroscience podcasts in the world. Unfiltered conversations from the trenches — with neurosurgeons, researchers, therapists, patients, and pioneers. Not just for doctors. For everyone who believes the brain deserves more than a passing mention.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="media-cta">Listen Now →</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Documentary -->
      <div class="media-card docu-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="media-icon-wrap docu-icon-wrap">
          <span class="media-emoji">🎥</span>
        </div>
        <div class="media-type-badge docu-badge">3-PART DOCUMENTARY</div>
        <h3 class="media-card-title">"Rebooting the Brain"</h3>
        <p class="media-card-sub">Streaming on YouTube</p>
        <p class="media-card-desc">
          Our philosophy narrated by Dr. Sharan & Dr. Pratibha. The dedication of the PRS Neurosciences team. Patient voices. Caregiver tears and triumphs. No statistic can explain what this docu-series captures — the human stories behind the science.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="media-cta">Watch Now →</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Beja Unfry -->
      <div class="media-card beja-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="media-icon-wrap beja-icon-wrap">
          <span class="media-emoji">🎬</span>
        </div>
        <div class="media-type-badge beja-badge">WEB SERIES</div>
        <h3 class="media-card-title">Beja Unfry</h3>
        <p class="media-card-sub">6-Episode Docu-Thriller · YouTube</p>
        <p class="media-card-desc">
          "Beja" = Brain. "Unfry" = bringing damaged brains back to life. A first-of-its-kind Indian medical docu-thriller in English — raw, real, and radically human. Based on Dr. Sharan's own journey from 8th grade dream to neurosurgeon. You will binge it. Guaranteed.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="media-cta">Watch Series →</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Radio -->
      <div class="media-card radio-card reveal">
        <div class="media-icon-wrap radio-icon-wrap">
          <span class="media-emoji">📻</span>
        </div>
        <div class="media-type-badge radio-badge">RADIO PROGRAM</div>
        <h3 class="media-card-title">"Rebooting the Brain"</h3>
        <p class="media-card-sub">92.7 BIG FM with Patpataki Sruti</p>
        <p class="media-card-desc">
          Bringing neuroscience to the airwaves — reaching diverse audiences across India, making brain health awareness mainstream and accessible to every listener.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="media-cta">Learn More →</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Research / Talks -->
      <div class="media-card talks-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="media-icon-wrap talks-icon-wrap">
          <span class="media-emoji">🌍</span>
        </div>
        <div class="media-type-badge talks-badge">GLOBAL SPEAKER</div>
        <h3 class="media-card-title">Conference Keynotes & Talks</h3>
        <p class="media-card-sub">Worldwide Stages · Digital Platforms</p>
        <p class="media-card-desc">
          From Instagram reels demystifying awake neurosurgery, to conference keynotes on circuit-based neurosurgery, to community talks for caregivers — Dr. Sharan doesn't communicate to impress. He communicates to empower. "Make people care about the brain before they're forced to."
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="media-cta">View Talks →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .media-section {
    background: var(--bg-slate);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .media-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(at 90% 10%, rgba(79,70,229,0.06) 0, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(at 10% 90%, rgba(6,182,212,0.05) 0, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .section-center {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .media-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 20px;
    background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1);
    color: var(--primary-color);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  .media-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .media-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .media-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .media-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 32px 28px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    transition: var(--transition-smooth);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .media-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-premium);
    border-color: rgba(79,70,229,0.15);
  }

  .media-icon-wrap {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .media-emoji { font-size: 1.8rem; }

  /* Icon backgrounds */
  .book-icon-wrap { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ede9fe, #ddd6fe); }
  .podcast-icon-wrap { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ecfdf5, #d1fae5); }
  .docu-icon-wrap { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7, #fde68a); }
  .beja-icon-wrap { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fee2e2, #fca5a5); }
  .radio-icon-wrap { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f2fe, #bae6fd); }
  .talks-icon-wrap { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f3e8ff, #e9d5ff); }

  /* Type badges */
  .media-type-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    background: rgba(79,70,229,0.1);
    color: var(--primary-color);
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  .podcast-badge { background: rgba(16,185,129,0.1); color: #059669; }
  .docu-badge { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.1); color: #d97706; }
  .beja-badge { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.1); color: #dc2626; }
  .radio-badge { background: rgba(6,182,212,0.1); color: #0284c7; }
  .talks-badge { background: rgba(126,34,206,0.1); color: var(--secondary-color); }

  .media-card-title {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-main);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .media-card-sub {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--accent-color);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .media-card-desc {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .media-cta {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: gap 0.3s, letter-spacing 0.3s;
    margin-top: 4px;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .media-cta:hover {
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    color: var(--secondary-color);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .media-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .media-title { font-size: 2.5rem; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .media-title { font-size: 2rem; }
    .media-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .media-card { padding: 24px 20px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .media-title { font-size: 1.75rem; }
  }
</style>
